</p>
<meta property="mw:PageProp/toc">
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Armijo_rule_and_curvature">Armijo rule and curvature</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wolfe_conditions&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Armijo rule and curvature"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>A step length <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \alpha _{k}}">
