</p>
<div><ol start="3" style="list-style-type:lower-roman"><li><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\big |}\mathbf {p} _{k}^{\mathrm {T} }\nabla f(\mathbf {x} _{k}+\alpha _{k}\mathbf {p} _{k}){\big |}\leq c_{2}{\big |}\mathbf {p} _{k}^{\mathrm {T} }\nabla f(\mathbf {x} _{k}){\big |}}">
